            "value": "예산"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Budgets drive the spending insights on your dashboard. Set a monthly limit for any category and you'll see progress + alerts when you're close to or over the limit.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "বাজেট আপনার ড্যাশবোর্ডের খরচের ইনসাইট পরিচালনা করে। যেকোনো ক্যাটেগরির জন্য মাসিক সীমা সেট করুন এবং সীমার কাছে বা বেশি হলে অগ্রগতি ও সতর্কতা দেখুন।"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Budgets drive the spending insights on your dashboard. Set a monthly limit for any category and you'll see progress + alerts when you're close to or over the limit."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los presupuestos impulsan los insights de gasto del panel. Establece un límite mensual para cualquier categoría y verás el progreso y alertas cuando te acerques o lo superes."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "予算はダッシュボードの支出インサイトを動かします。任意のカテゴリに月次上限を設定すると、進捗と上限近くまたは超過時のアラートが表示されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "预算驱动仪表盘上的支出洞察。为任何类别设置月度限额，您将看到进度和接近或超过限额时的提醒。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "예산은 대시보드의 지출 인사이트를 구동합니다. 카테고리에 월별 한도를 설정하면 진행 상황과 한도에 가까워지거나 초과할 때 알림을 받게 됩니다."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Built since closing · %@": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "bn": {
